TO:E.SUN BANK
三
四
D
The irrevocable credit as follows:(Hereinafter called the “Credit")
It is agreed and understood that this credit is subject to ICC's "Uniform Customs and Practice for Documentary Credits" (version
in force on the date of issuance of the letter of credit concerned).
>
玉山銀行 轉讓信用狀修改申請書
APPLICATION FOR AMENDMENT OF IRREVOCABLE CREDIT TRANSFER
>
□有換單轉讓 With Substitution of Documents
□不換單轉讓 Without Substitution of Documents
基本資料:
Basic Information :
Transferee / Second Beneficiary Name/ Tel./ Add.
(受讓人 / 第二受益人名稱/電話/地址)
Original L/C Issued by
(開狀銀行)
New expiry date :
(修改轉讓信用狀有效期限)
New latest shipment date:
(修改最遲裝運日)
Other amendments(其他修改事項):
茲向貴行申請修改上述轉讓信用狀,修改項目如下:
You are kindly requested to make the following amendments to the subject transferred credit :
Transferred credit Increased Decreased by]
making new total amount 幣別
(增加/減少轉讓信用狀金額)
其他條款及條件不變。
All other terms and conditions remain unchanged.
外匯服務中心
核章 經辦
Transfer No.:
受理單位
核章 經辦
Amount Transferred
(轉讓金額)
幣別
Original L/C No.
(信用狀編號)
費用承擔 Charges
Please indicate “X” in n whichever is applicable (請選擇適當者,並註明"X"於空格)
The transferring amendment charges are for our account. (修改費用由本公司承擔)
The transferring amendment charges are for account of transferee. (修改費用由第二受益人承擔)
Other(其他):
驗印
【電子信箱進件專用】
For E-mail Application Only
